      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS for a sharp, linear power band. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers precise engagement, paired with a factory-equipped M Variable Differential Lock for superior corner-exit traction. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the structural integrity of the chassis. The suspension geometry remains tight with refreshed bushings, while the exterior displays a light patina consistent with a well-enjoyed enthusiast vehicle. Mechanically robust and ready for spirited use, this M3 represents a balanced intersection of performance and reliability.",
